&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Intake. &lt;/strong&gt;The integrity of the intake process — ensuring every project enters with a clear, complete brief and a named owner before work begins, and that the AI-assisted intake tooling is used and kept useful.&lt;/li&gt;
